libnotify: The Desktop Notifications framework
libnotify:
libnotify: The Desktop Notifications framework provides a standard way of
libnotify: doing passive pop-up notifications on the Linux desktop. These
libnotify: are designed to notify the user of something without interrupting
libnotify: their work with a dialog box that they must close. Passive
libnotify: popups can automatically disappear after a short period of time.
libnotify: 
libnotify: This project consists of a specification
libnotify: (http://www.galago.info/specs/notification/index.php) and a
libnotify: reference implementation (libnotify and notification-daemon).
